						               													<description>ReelGenius is a game that puts you and your friends in the roll of a big-time Hollywood producer.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Starting with $15 million in cash, you must &amp;quot;make your movie&amp;quot; by acquiring your four required movie elements: a Screenplay, a Director, a Lead Player, and a Supporting Cast&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But making your movie is only half the battle&amp;hellip;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Next you must release your movie nationwide&amp;hellip;score big at the box office&amp;hellip;and take home more ReelGenius movie awards than your opponents &amp;ndash; and while avoiding the scandals and pitfalls that can sink your film in a hurry.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Just how successful you are depends on how shrewdly you manage your movie&amp;rsquo;s budget&amp;hellip;how savvy you are in acquiring talent&amp;hellip;and on your ability to wheel and deal your way to the top.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But that&amp;rsquo;s not all&amp;hellip;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your ability to answer creatively-crafted movie questions can make or break you. And just like real-life Hollywood, you&amp;rsquo;ll have to deal with negative publicity, scathing reviews and all the other things that can hinder your movie&amp;rsquo;s success.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Two to 6 players or teams can play ReelGenius in under an hour or over several. You decide how long the game will last by deciding how many ReelGenius movie award statues you want to play for.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;ReelGenius comes with a game board, $330 million in ReelGenius cash, 32 talent cards, 24 &amp;quot;Player&amp;quot; cards, 24 &amp;quot;Publicity&amp;quot; cards, 1800 movie questions of varying difficulty, 30 ReelGenius Awards, 6 gme tokens, 2 game dice, and rules sheet.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
